1DC28350.Line13.121C9F: I cannot thank you enough for this, stranger. Truly, thank you.

411C4632.VoiceDir9.121C9F: Talking about people nearby, loud enough for them to hear

453ED98E.Line11.121C9F: There is a bridge leading into the wetlands. Meet me there. I must go ready myself.

8ED7735D.Line1.121C9F: You would risk the dangers of the swamp? For a stranger, no less? It seems the Light does still shine, even in the swamps of Hawezar.

9037BCFF.VoiceDir5.140002: Knowing you should do something, but still not wanting to.

F0E61A65.Line9.121C9F: Though, I would not need the kindness of a stranger if the Zakarum Crusaders had any fight left in them.
